+### MC-071: Viz Views, Data Shape, and Plan State Derivation
+
+Spec sections:
+
+- `docs/specs/rhei-viz.spec.md` -> `Views`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-viz.spec.md` -> `Level-Grouped Axis Rules (Gantt)`
