+### MC-002: State Machine Schema Used By Commands
+
+Spec sections:
+
+- `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md` -> `Schema Additions`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md` -> `Top-level fields`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md` -> `Per-state fields`
